{"TopicId":188869,"ForumId":109,"TopicTitle":"What atmospheric effects will ksp 2 have?","CreatedByName":"KrakenNinja","CreatedById":190459,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-13T12:06:14Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"KrakenNinja","CreatedById":190459,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-13T12:06:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat atmospheric effects will ksp 2 have? Clouds? Fog?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pandaman","CreatedById":130621,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-13T12:28:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAFAIK nothing confirmed, or even seriously hinted at, yet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPersonally, I think not\u00A0having clouds would be a bit of an oversight.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xd the great","CreatedById":188222,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-13T13:10:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes supersonic condensation clouds, as found in the trailer, count?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pandaman","CreatedById":130621,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-13T13:23:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223686561\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221570972204\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022188222\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xd the great\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 minutes ago, Xd the great said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes supersonic condensation clouds, as found in the trailer, count?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot for me, KSP1 has vapour trails, but not \u0027normal\u0027 clouds.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kaerbanogue","CreatedById":189143,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-13T13:55:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDevs did not talk about atmospheric features. Ok we haven\u0027t seen atmospheric effects in the pre-alpha gameplay footage but we do have seen clouds on screenshots devs released. So for now it\u0027s likely that KSP2 will feature at least clouds but we can\u0027t be sure since we have no official confirmation.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn response to \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/188222-xd-the-great/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022188222\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/188222-xd-the-great/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Xd the great\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223686561\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221570972204\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022188222\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xd the great\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n33 minutes ago, Xd the great said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes supersonic condensation clouds, as found in the trailer, count?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVery interesting point here, I had to rewatch the trailer to spot the contrails.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust my opinion but I think that could be a thing. As for dust, nobody would have thought that dust could have been a feature according to e3 trailer whereas we know now (thanks to DasValdez live) that it was a hint... So yes contrails could definitely be a thing...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0chemtrails\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xd the great","CreatedById":188222,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-13T23:05:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223686581\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221570974903\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022189143\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kaerbanogue\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, Kaerbanogue said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022#\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/a\u003E \u003Cspan\u003EHide contents\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0chemtrails\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nShhhhh.\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\nI have interest in sending kerbals into this \u0022trail\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Commodore_32","CreatedById":200414,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-13T23:11:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think that the devs will focus more in the space scenery than the kerbin atmosphere and scenery.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo we will expect more changes in space than atmosphere.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-13T23:43:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223686782\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221571008291\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022200414\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Commodoregamer118\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n30 minutes ago, Commodoregamer118 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think that the devs will focus more in the space scenery than the kerbin atmosphere and scenery.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo we will expect more changes in space than atmosphere.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClouds on planets *are* space scenery.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Commodore_32","CreatedById":200414,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-13T23:47:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223686791\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221571010198\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClouds on planets *are* space scenery.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI did not meant that. The clouds viewed from space are essential to make a good look.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI meant *IN* the atmosphere.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-13T23:49:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223686793\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221571010423\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022200414\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Commodoregamer118\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Commodoregamer118 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI did not meant that. The clouds viewed from space are essential to make a good look.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI meant *IN* the atmosphere.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would be weird to have clouds disappear as you enter an atmosphere.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know how weird as I\u0027ve not experienced it, but it would be weird.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Commodore_32","CreatedById":200414,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-13T23:53:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223686795\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022188869\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221571010566\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would be weird to have clouds disappear as you enter an atmosphere.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know how weird as I\u0027ve not experienced it, but it would be weird.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI dont think so. It will be totally weird.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think that will be something like when you enter the clouds are in there. But when you are descending you cross the clouds and they will stay at a high altitude.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpaceCube2000","CreatedById":163416,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-14T01:00:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe director of the game stated in an interview that they would like clouds in the game; therefore, it\u0027s very possible that they will add that feature. With regards to atmospheric fog, in the gameplay footage that we\u0027ve seen so far, it seems that fog will be an atmospheric effect.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}